12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 82 O.S. 2021, Section 1020.19, is
14 amended to read as follows:
15 Section 1020.19. Upon request of a majority of the landowners
16 residing within a basin or subbasin, the Board is authorized to
17 require that water wells be metered and that such meters as the
18 Board shall approve be utilized by the applicant and placed under
19 seal, subject to reading by the agents of the Board at any time.
20 The Board may also require that the applicant report the reading of
21 such meters at reasonable intervals
22 A. To encourage groundwater conservation, beginning January 1,
23 2026, the Board shall provide a five-year flex allocation of
24 groundwater usage based off the previously determined allocated
